The paper focuses on the development of an analytics tool for exploring scientific software and related publications, which suggests that it falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and digital libraries (cs.DL) sub-categories. The tool involves automatic code discovery, which could also relate to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). Additionally, the tool could potentially involve database systems (cs.DB) for managing and organizing the software and publication data.
